e the fixed income instruments cic purchases are typically of intermediateterm duration and may be laddered for different maturity dates they may also invest clients funds in a money market fund website httpwwwcicinvestmentscom in the news see more denver business journal february   team of financial professionals at bbva compass unit decamps for united capital marketwired october   goodman gold trust renews issuer bid executives  employees steve john dreiling chief executive officer brian michael mcdowell chief investment officer keenan mcneace chief operations officer gayle godfrey administrative coordinator bob bush director of fixed income  economics larry james hilton portfolio manager lisa schwinghammer portfolio manager clark david johnson portfolio manager joel gregory johnson portfolio manager chris johnson portfolio manager see our list of current and previous employees when you upgrade start my free trial â¤ see more board of directors clark david johnson portfolio manager at capital investment counsel inc see our list of current and previous board members when you upgrade start my free trial â¤ see more paths to capital investment counsel inc capital investment counsel inc you connections via relationship science capital investment counsel inc sync your contacts to see how you can connect with capital investment counsel inc start my free trial â¤ see more recent transactions details hidden compass bancshares inc purchases capital investment counsel inc awards  honors rank   financial planning magazine  top rias sponsored by source media holdings inc youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial â¤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci proÂ  â¤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in loginÂ  â¤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis term